title: potion of immovability
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

After drinking this slightly metallic potion, you become magically fixed in place (in the frame of reference you were in when you drank it) for 1 minute. You cannot move, even if you are defying gravity. You can support up to 8,000 pounds of weight. More weight causes the effect to fail and end.